ğŸ” Security Best Practice (Recommended)

Instead of giving full bucket access, you can restrict to table path only:

"Resource": [
  "arn:aws:s3:::prod-bucket/warehouse/db/table",
  "arn:aws:s3:::prod-bucket/warehouse/db/table/*"
]


This is more secure for production.

âœ… Final Summary

